# bokcolmaps

### Colour map plots based on the Bokeh visualisation library

----------

Get started with:

import numpy  
from bokcolmaps.plot_colourmap import plot_colourmap  
data = numpy.random.rand(3, 4, 5)  
plot_colourmap(data)

or see bokcolmaps.Examples.plot_colourmap_example
